kafka for Debian
----------------
This package is created using kafka binary release

How to build this package
-------------------------

Download kafka to parenet direcotry
    ../kafka_2.10-0.8.2.1.tgz

Set SCALA_VERSION and KAFKA_VERSION
    export SCALA_VERSION=2.10
    export KAFKA_VERSION=0.8.2.1

Build debian package
    dpkg-buildpackage -b -uc -us
